name: Nejire Embedding (BNHA)
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding to generate Nejire (BNHA) character. Use nejire to activate.

Example images generated using Latte which you can grab here: https://huggingface.co/andite/yohan-diffusion/blob/main/Latte.safetensors

Trained on NAI so works best with models/mixes based on that.
